<div><head>周易繫辭明氏注</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.2">繫辭上傳</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.3">通乎晝夜之道而知。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.4">「知」音智。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.5">陸德明《釋文》引荀爽、荀柔之、明僧紹。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.6">《易》有君子之道四焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.7">《釋文》「聖人之道」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-1a.8">明僧紹作「君子之道」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.2">繫辭下傳</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.3">何以守位？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.4">曰仁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.5">《釋文》「曰人」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1026_CHANT_001-2a.6">王肅、卞伯玉、桓元、明僧紹作「仁」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
